divs: Sighting DetailsDidn't see actual UFO my daughter and I saw and "X" and a "!" in the NW sky. It was really weird. Did not look like Jet trail. I have been around military bases my whole life and this did not look like something that was "written" or even maybe by chance. It was pretty neat though. i tried to take a picture of it, but it would not show up on my phone. Maybe it was a cloud formation, but never seen one so clear cut. It was picture perfect.
